020-05-21|accessdate=2020-11-15|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811101359/https://game.ettoday.net/article/1719808.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 评论 ===
对于真希波在剧中的表现，评论者褒贬不一。布莱恩·莫顿于Fandom Post发表评论称自己喜欢这个角色，一方面是因为她的个性，另一方面是因为她给这个熟悉的故事带来了不确定性，是新剧场版系列走向原创的重要标志<ref>{{cite web |author=Bryan Morton |title=Evangelion 2.22: You Can (Not) Advance UK Anime Blu-ray Review |url=https://www.fandompost.com/2011/08/12/evangelion-2-22-you-can-not-advance-uk-anime-blu-ray-review/ |website=The Fandom Post |date=2011-08-12 |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2012-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323162742/http://www.fandompost.com/2011/08/12/evangelion-2-22-you-can-not-advance-uk-anime-blu-ray-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。真希波被认为是最神秘的EVA驾驶员，拥有易于分辨的外形，乐天轻佻的性格让她显得与众不同<ref>{{cite web |author=Andrew Hamlin |title="Evangelion 2.0" worthy of its predecessor |url=http://nwasianweekly.com/2011/01/%E2%80%9Cevangelion-2-0%E2%80%9D-worthy-of-its-predecessor/ |website=Northwest Asian Weekly |date=2011-01-20 |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2016-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160712083259/http://nwasianweekly.com/2011/01/%e2%80%9cevangelion-2-0%e2%80%9d-worthy-of-its-predecessor/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。Fandom Post的克里斯·霍默表示，真希波是唯一一个享受战斗的EVA驾驶员，这一点很吸引人；同时他也指出，角色缺乏发展，似乎只是用来迎合[[爱好者|粉丝]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Chris Homer |title=Top 10 British Characters In Anime |url=https://www.fandompost.com/2015/04/26/top-10-british-characters-in-anime/ |website=The Fandom Post |date=2015-04-26 |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2019-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191002163121/https://www.fandompost.com/2015/04/26/top-10-british-characters-in-anime/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。VG Cultural HQ的摩根·路易斯非常欣赏《福音戰士新劇場版》，但讨厌真希波，他认为真希波只是一个迎合粉丝的[[殺必死|殺必死]]角色却夺走了[[加持良治|加持良治]]的最佳场景<ref>{{cite web |author=Morgan Lewis |title=Evangelion 3.0+1.0 Anime Expo Screening Time Revealed |url=http://vgculturehq.com/evangelion-3-01-0-anime-expo-screening-time-revealed/ |website=VG Culture HQ |date=2019-07-03 |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107223643/http://vgculturehq.com/evangelion-3-01-0-anime-expo-screening-time-revealed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。CBR.com的勒南·方特斯指出，真希波虽然参演了两部电影，但仍然没有任何实质内容<ref>{{cite web |author=Renan Fontes |title=Rebuild Of Evangelion: 5 Ways It Improves On The Original Anime (& 5 Ways It Doesn't) |url=https://www.cbr.com/rebuild-of-evangelion-improves-original-doesnt/ |website=CBR |date=2019-11-26 |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023233145/https://www.cbr.com/rebuild-of-evangelion-improves-original-doesnt/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。THEM动画评论网的尼科莱塔·布朗也表达了类似的观点，她认为真希波之于剧情无关紧要<ref>{{cite web |author=Nicoletta Christina Browne |title=Review - Evangelion 2.0: You Can (Not) Advance |url=http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=1385 |website=THEM Anime Reviews |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2018-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180802011601/http://www.themanime.org/viewreview.php?id=1385 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在剧中，甚至连她的全名都没有被提及<ref>{{cite web |author=Andy Hanley |title=Evangelion 2.22: You Can (Not) Advance Review |url=http://www.uk-anime.net/anime/Evangelion_2.22:_You_Can_(Not)_Advance.html |website=UK Anime Network |date=2011-06-15 |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2015-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403235020/http://uk-anime.net/anime/Evangelion_2.22:_You_Can_(Not)_Advance.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]的马克·松比洛批评道，真希波几乎没有角色发展，她的许多元素侵占原明日香的领域，她的存在纯粹是为了推出新商品<ref>{{cite web |author=Mark Sombillo |title=Evangelion: 2.22 You Can (Not) Advance - Review |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/evangelion-2.22-you-can-not-advance |website=Anime News Network |date=2011-06-07 |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2018-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180315201424/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/evangelion-2.22-you-can-not-advance |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同样来自動畫新聞網的塞隆·马丁评论说，「活泼热情的真希波与既有的EVA驾驶员形成鲜明对比，以至于她的加入让人觉得不协调，但这很可能是关键：她被用来突破既有的框架，表明不是只有人格障碍者才能驾驶EVA。尽管她在两部电影的战斗场景中扮演着重要角色，但是没有足够的戏份让观众了解她的动机和目的。不过，她是商业行销所需要的新鲜空气，有助于补充原系列所具有的神秘感。」<ref name=Martin>{{cite web |author=Theron Martin |title=Evangelion 2.22: You Can (Not) Advance BLURAY - Review |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/evangelion-2.22/you-can-not-advance/bluray |website=Anime News Network |date=2011-03-31 |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-17 |archive-date=2018-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615175808/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/evangelion-2.22/you-can-not-advance/bluray |dead-url=no }}</ref>许多评论觉得新角色真希波的加入是因为制作方有意迎合大众的喜好，但是导演鹤卷和哉在访谈中否定了这种说法。鹤卷表示，这种看法只是结果论，实际创作中完全不是这样{{Sfn|庵野秀明|轟木一騎|2010|p=348|loc=§鶴卷和哉interview}}。

